txt.en: Across the Ettenmoors, the enemies of the Free People rampage. Take up your arms and defeat the enemy. You shall be rewarded for your efforts.
Report your efforts to Captain-General Tordúr
Battle in the Ettenmoors continues. Your contributions to the battle will earn you a great reward.
Having beaten back the forces of Angmar, it is now time to claim your spoils. Return to Glàn Vraig and speak with Captain-general Tordúr to claim your rewards.

'It is good to see you again, [placeholder]. Your deeds echo through the ranks of my forces. You are a formidable opponent and I am grateful to count you as an ally against the growing darkness in this land.'
Completed Battle Task: To the Front! ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Complete Battle Task: To the Front! ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Fight in the Ettenmoors until you eliminated a great number of enemies. Then you can reap your rewards from the Captain-general at Glán Vraig.
'Your effort here is great. Yet it can still be more. Return to me when you have handled all I ask.'
